value.string: Breathtaking views of Molokai and Kalohi channel from this centrally located 3 bedroom, 3 ½ bath residence at Montage, Kapalua Bay. This deeded, one-twelfth fractional ownership interest gives you 21 deeded days a year plus access to additional days on a per diem basis. Your fixed time is two consecutive weeks in Mid June each year (weeks 23 & 24) plus one float week (encompassing the 1st week in January through the 1st week in February or Thanksgiving week). This owner ship is one of only five interests that were sold with this premium time in June. Every day on property you will be pampered by the Montage staff, the twice daily housekeeping, your assigned concierge, not to mention the in-residence dining, signature restaurant, kids programs, lagoon pools and much much more. Association dues are paid through 2017. 2016: Jan. 9 – Jan.16 & June 4 – June 18 2017: Jan. 21 – Jan.28 & June 10 – June 24 2018: Jan. 27 – Feb.3 & June 9 – June 23 2019: Feb. 2 – Feb.9 & June 8 – June 22
House with detached ohana across the street from park and close to the Golf Course. May be non-conforming issues but a great opportunity for large extended family.

This is a great clean single level home in North Kihei. Low maintance yard and a one car garage. A block away from the beach and a convenient location when driving to Central Maui or the West Side. Added extended driveway for additional parking. All offers are to be submitted through Auction Company. Contact your local Realtor for information. After auction concludes, it may take up to 7 calendar days for offer decision. Communication will be sent to bidders with results & next steps for the accepted offer. Property subject to $2,000 buyer premium paid at closing. Bank of America, N.A. employees, employees’ household members and HTS business partners of the Bank are prohibited from purchasing this property, whether directly or indirectly. This is being sold "AS IS". Include AS IS Addendum. No Seller's Real Property Disclosure provided. NO TERMITE INSPECTION OR RELATED SERVICES PROVIDED BY SELLER, NO SURVEY, NO CLEANING, NO HOA/CONDO DOCS, NO REPAIRS PROVIDED BY SELLER.

Welcome to Hana and to this 4BR 2 Bath home on a half acre lot conveniently located as you come in to town. Home has spacious kitchen, living and family rooms together with a big front, side and backyards. This home is close to the beach, the Hana schools, airport and the business centre of Hana town.

Lender sale see realtor remarks for details of the lender auction. Large 3 bedroom 3 bath home with over 2100 square feet of living space located in the desirable Greens subdivision. The lot is over 7,000 square feet, large garage, in ground pool, and beautiful views of the Maui Lani golf course. With a little tender loving care this could be your Maui Dream home. Please see realtor remarks for details on lender auction.

Three bedroom, two bath home in Piilani Village I, a great community with mature tree lined streets and easy access to the Piilani Hwy. Located near the Kihei Community Center and Pool, Piilani Shopping Village, schools, dining and the world famous white sand beaches of South Maui. The house requires some TLC and that has been reflected in the price. The large lot is waiting for your landscape touches to make it into the tropical paradise it can be.

One of the few properties in Waiehu Terrace that has a huge yard. Conveniently located near schools, grocery stores, churches, parks, public facilities and minutes away from the beach! Property is occupied and occupants are not to be disturbed or contacted under any circumstances. Interior inspections are not available and property is being sold as is. Property is sold through auction. Please contact your local Realtor for details.
Great Potential! Three dwellings on a large lot upcountry Maui! Being sold As Is Easy to show!!

Great floor plan with spacious lot. This ranch style five-bedroom home is centrally located, close to all of the conveniences. The home has been updated with fresh paint inside and out, new carpets, new garage door, and all plumbing and electrical has been inspected and repaired/brought to code by licensed contractors. Buyer may use any lender to obtain financing for the purchase.

This Fannie Mae, single family home has been creatively re-arranged for extended living areas. The front area is a "family room" with 3 bedrooms and a bath. The far, right back is 1.5 stories and consists of 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths. Open living area to the kitchen. The permitted bonus area at the far left has 2 bedrooms and a bath. Per Hawaii State Law, no seller's disclosure will be given. Property being sold in "as is" condition. Easy to show.

HOUSE AND COTTAGE!!!!! Great deal in the heart of kihei. Main house is 3 bedroom 2 baths and a 2 bed 1 bath cottage sitting on 9433 sq.ft of land Your Next Home is located close to the beach and shopping and local restaurants. Very easy to show! NO FHA LOANS.

This Fannie Mae, multi-dwelling property is conveniently located almost half way between S. Kihei Rd and Pililani Hwy for easy access in all directions. A short walking distance to Cove Beach Park. As you enter the property, the 1 bedroom, 1 bath cottage is first, followed by the 3 bedroom, 3 bath house which includes a family room at the back. Wood floors, walls and ceiling in the house with many decks around it. Concrete tile roofs. Easy to show.

This spacious Fannie Mae home is at the top of Maui Meadows. It is a Single Family Residential Condo. The original half+ acre lot was legally separated into 2 sections. The front dwelling/house (B) is at the top of the driveway, closest to the street. The cottage (A) is at the bottom of the driveway. There is one water meter for both units, but separate electric meters. CPR documents spell out how costs are divided. The main living room is on the 2nd floor with beautiful, open beam ceilings. The "open" floor plan has the dining area and kitchen at one side that opens on to a large deck. A 1/2 bath and master bedroom and bath at the other end of the house. Downstairs has a large family room, 2 bathrooms, and 2 bedrooms. On the contract, the address should be written as: 803 Kumulani Dr B. Easy to show.
